{"tid":2108100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟計畫採取「協調」行動支持香港自治","createTime":"2020-07-14T10:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T10:11:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d910c4c2c2149cb949a125fc0c2f1e1917fb456","tid":2108100,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5fSc4isKI1C5iaW4MM4tlQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/6de60410-c55e-11ea-b75d-212f8c8cda6c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5fSc4isKI1C5iaW4MM4tlQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2F6de60410-c55e-11ea-b75d-212f8c8cda6c&h=ad52c0fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【彭博】-- 歐盟最高外交官員稱，該地區將「協調」歐盟層面和成員國層面的措施來支持香港自治，以對抗中國在這個亞洲金融中心實施的新國家安全法。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟外交政策負責人Josep Borrell稱中國頒布的新國安法太「嚴厲」，歐盟可能採取的回應措施包括提高香港學生獎學金，為香港居民提供更寬鬆的簽證安排，並對用於執法的「特殊和敏感技術」出口採取限制。<br />\n<br />\n「在接下來幾天，一些成員國可能宣布作為該計畫一部分的國家層面的措施，」Borrell周一在主持召開歐盟27國外交部長會議後對記者表示。「我們將繼續支持香港人民。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/歐盟計畫採取-協調-行動支持香港自治-160941862.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96-%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF-%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB-160941862.html&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=13ce73b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/歐盟計畫採取-協調-行動支持香港自治-160941862.html</a>"},{"pid":"49542c166e9f4441a26100cc2d734444adb0c5c0","tid":2108100,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一日有東德肥婆一日都唔會有咩發生"},{"pid":"03dfe4542b2c100bad7d30d3f6191075e802ba5b","tid":2108100,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}